Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.36,0:10:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}它會侵蝕你的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}折磨你 虐待你 詛咒你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.82,0:10:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人類的身體無法抑制它
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.31,0:10:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你的身體恐怕遲早會毀掉的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.52,0:10:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的身體還能撐多久？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}其實…我活到今天一直背負著兩個詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.17,0:10:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一個是夜之愛子的這具身體
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有一個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:11:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大概只要我活著 這份詛咒就不會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.64,0:11:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在再多一個詛咒 也沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.56,0:11:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.39,0:11:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那樣是在生氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.48,0:11:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 我不會請求你原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請不要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.05,0:11:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是一種證明
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.94,0:11:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是我能夠為他人著想的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.67,0:11:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你也可以選擇到那邊生活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.00,0:11:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.26,0:11:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會考慮的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.71,0:11:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.00,0:11:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣好嗎 你可能會無法維持人類的形態啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.89,0:11:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我做好了最壞的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.89,0:11:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是在意自己外表的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.89,0:14:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你跑出來沒問題嗎 還是偷跑出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我更喜歡室外的空氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.01,0:14:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼你還笑得出來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.88,0:14:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你什麼時候發現的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.65,0:14:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你想從窗戶翻出去 還在空中滾了一圈的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那不是從一開始就知道了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的小狗好像變笨了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我以前只是裝作很懂事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.58,0:14:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}之前沒說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.08,0:14:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}出門都忘了告訴我一聲 現在倒挺會說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但你也沒有答覆我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.62,0:15:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是在整理
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.73,0:15:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}花了一整天嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.40,0:15:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你總是想要一個人遠去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明總是你向我伸出手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.27,0:15:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}握住我的手叫我回家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.93,0:15:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然而卻又如此漫不經心地 要拋下我離開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.81,0:15:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也不是馬上就會死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你怎麼會這麼樂觀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.82,0:15:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道你總有一天會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明應該阻止你的 但我卻沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在心中某個角落 我總覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.70,0:15:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你會一直待在那個家裡 今後也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.87,0:15:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想著你一定不會有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.18,0:16:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.20,0:16:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.45,0:16:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}起初我們只是互相利用的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.06,0:16:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}光是一起生活竟變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我有過不想活的念頭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.43,0:16:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可是 我受到了許多人的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.32,0:16:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}知道了自己也是能對別人伸出援手的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.66,0:16:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不再是等著別人給自己庇護
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.58,0:16:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我有了留在這裡做點事的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.88,0:16:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}自我犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.09,0:16:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你覺得毀掉自己就能得到留在這裡的資格嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.28,0:16:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.12,0:16:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我自己也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.51,0:16:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這次也只是因為有能力去做而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.35,0:17:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我沒撒謊 人類有自己弄不懂的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.86,0:17:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再說 你的小狗是個傻瓜嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.32,0:17:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}行動比思考要快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.68,0:17:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你願意和我這樣的傻瓜一起思考嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}思考我能在留在你身邊的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我沒辦法像你這樣擅長行動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.47,0:17:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但我可以陪你去確認一些事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.44,0:17:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過要記得帶我一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.38,0:17:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一定要找到 一定要思考
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.22,0:17:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有什麼方法能幫自己前進
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.91,0:17:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我叫瑪莉艾爾 山羊牧人瑪莉艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.81,0:18:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在是一名魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}競拍會上的交易？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是的 我幫她提供資金
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.13,0:18:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然後她回饋我龍血的交易
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.75,0:18:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看來是不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.32,0:18:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你那是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.11,0:18:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只是看看而已 真是保護過度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.83,0:18:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}瑪莉艾爾小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.13,0:18:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.21,0:18:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}光輝萬丈的大地女神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}撕裂毒蛇的風暴之神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.59,0:18:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}您的貴手 您的玉目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.88,0:18:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請容我借用片刻光陰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.07,0:19:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這些是什麼啊 真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.80,0:19:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是龍的詛咒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.41,0:19:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你有興趣當魔女嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.51,0:19:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}詛咒是魔女的專長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.90,0:19:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}成為我們的夥伴 加入魔女會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.16,0:19:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家也許能幫到你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.09,0:19:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.15,0:19:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你有信心指引女性的人生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.36,0:19:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}瑪莉艾爾小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.17,0:19:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要成為你們的夥伴 我需要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.13,0:19:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.37,0:19:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}總之你先來集會做客吧 越早越好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.71,0:20:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}下好決心之後 就打開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.50,0:20:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我等你的回覆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.29,0:20:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.07,0:20:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}天啊 那孩子還那麼小
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.20,0:20:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}給你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.42,0:20:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}卡片？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.79,0:20:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我生日會的邀請函
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.43,0:20:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世什麼時候過生日
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.52,0:20:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.44,0:20:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天？為什麼不慶生？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.98,0:20:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你為什麼不幫她辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.21,0:20:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}慶生會…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.55,0:20:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是的 明年可要考慮好怎麼慶祝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.25,0:21:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 明年…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.89,0:21:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.16,0:21:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}突然想吐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.21,0:21:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我去個洗手間 你先坐一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.23,0:21:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我只是來送邀請卡的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.65,0:21:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.81,0:21:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.12,0:21:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好不容易不想死了 居然就碰上這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.69,0:21:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去魔女的集會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.75,0:21:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.83,0:21:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你的弟子 可能活不過接下來的春天了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.18,0:21:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想辦法治癒你的身體才是當務之急
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.13,0:21:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.04,0:22:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}畢竟還要去想明年生日會怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.10,0:22:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}龍的詛咒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.49,0:22:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我身上不死的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.97,0:22:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}與你身上必死的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.68,0:22:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}搞不好還很速配哦
Comment: 0,0:22:24.85,0:22:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,ED-FF FINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.00,0:22:33.01,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}月は見ていた　欠けてる僕ら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.13,0:22:37.67,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}互いを呼び合いながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.98,0:22:47.18,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}遠回りで　遠い道を歩いた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.36,0:22:57.47,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}引きよせ合う　赤と黒が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.62,0:23:04.07,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}追いかけ合う　闇と光が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.36,0:23:10.25,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}二つの対なるもので
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.44,0:23:12.89,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}創られてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.89,0:23:16.22,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}この世の総べては
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.53,0:23:23.16,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}あなたがいるから私はいる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.59,0:23:29.45,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}離れてもそばにいる（そばにいる）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.45,0:23:35.87,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}誰もが自分の　もう一つの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.09,0:23:42.02,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}片割れという　大切なもの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.02,0:23:50.06,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}探し続けてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.00,0:22:33.01,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}望著月亮 殘缺的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.13,0:22:37.67,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}互相呼喚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.98,0:22:47.18,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}選擇了遠路 並肩啟程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.36,0:22:57.47,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}互相吸引的紅與黑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.62,0:23:04.07,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}相互追趕的光與暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.36,0:23:10.25,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}對立的兩種存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.44,0:23:12.89,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}創造出了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.89,0:23:16.22,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}世間的芳華絢爛
